'''克莉絲汀·福克斯'''（{{lang-en|Christine Fox}}），曾任[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]代理副部長，是美國史上迄今位階最高的女性國防部官員。曾任美國國防部計畫暨預算評估署署長，是美國國防部的最資深文職官員之一，2013年12月，歐巴馬總統命任她為美國國防部代理副部長，直到2014年2月[[羅伯特·沃克|羅伯特·沃克]]（Robert Orton Work）接任副部長為止。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/12/03/21742320-top-gun-inspiration-becomes-highest-ranking-woman-at-pentagon|title='Top Gun' inspiration becomes highest-ranking woman at Pentagon - NBC News|accessdate=2014-02-20|date=2013-12-03|publisher=Usnews.nbcnews.com|archive-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130235736/http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/12/03/21742320-top-gun-inspiration-becomes-highest-ranking-woman-at-pentagon|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年5月，克莉絲汀·福克斯自美國國防部退休。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2014/05/07/statement-president-retirement-christine-h-fox|title=Statement by the President on the Retirement of Christine H. Fox | The White House|accessdate=2014-07-14|date=2014-05-07|publisher=Whitehouse.gov|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013071700/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2014/05/07/statement-president-retirement-christine-h-fox|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==逸事==
她曾服務於[[美國海軍陸戰隊米拉瑪航空站|美國海軍陸戰隊米拉瑪航空站]]（Marine Corps Air Station Miramar），根據《時人》雜誌報導，[[捍衛戰士|捍衛戰士]]的製片曾與她訪談，並以她為原型，塑造出捍衛戰士中的女教官查莉這個角色。<ref name="People">{{Cite web | url = https://people.com/archive/air-warfare-expert-christine-fox-fighter-pilots-call-her-legs-inspires-the-new-movie-top-gun-vol-24-no-6/ | title = Air Warfare Expert Christine Fox—Fighter Pilots Call Her "Legs"—Inspires the New Movie Top Gun | language = en | last = Richman | first = Alan | year = 1985 | publisher = [[時人_(雜誌)|People]] | date = 1985-08-05 | accessdate = 2020-07-16 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015310/https://people.com/archive/air-warfare-expert-christine-fox-fighter-pilots-call-her-legs-inspires-the-new-movie-top-gun-vol-24-no-6/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://scoopdeck.navytimes.com/2013/12/06/christine-fox-from-legs-to-top-woman-at-the-pentagon/ | title = Christine Fox, from 'Legs' to top woman at the Pentagon | language = en | last = Myers | first = Meghann | year = 2013 | publisher = Nevy Times | date = 2013-12-06 | accessdate = 2020-07-16 }}</ref>

